high_descs: Go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the knife off of the counter.
Go to the counter on the other side of the sink with the potato.
Cut the potato with the knife.
Take the knife to the fridge.
Put the knife inside the fridge.
Go back to the potato.
Grab a slice of potato from the counter.
Take the potato to the fridge.
Put the potato in and then take it back out.
Take the potato back to the counter.
Place the potato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Cut and refrigerate the potato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the end of the counter and turn to your left.
Pick up the butter knife on the edge of the counter.
Turn to your left and go to the counter to the left of the sink.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Turn around and do to the end of the counter that wraps around, then turn to your left and go to the refrigerator.
Place the knife in the refrigerator, on the top shelf, in front of the bowl.
Turn around and go back to the end of the counter that stick out from the kitchen, then turn to your right and go back to the counter across from you, where the potato is.
Pick up one of the potato slices on the counter.
Turn around and go back to the end of the counter that wraps around and turn to your left and go to the refrigerator.
Place the potato slice in the refrigerator, on the top shelf, to the left of the knife, wait a moment for the potato slice to chill, then remove the potato slice from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go back to the counter that sticks out from the kitchen, turn to your right and go back to the counter across from you where the rest of the potato is.
Place the potato slice on the counter to the left of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in the refrigerator, and a cold potato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the potato on the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Turn right and step forward to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Turn left and step forward to face the potato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Turn right and step forward to face the fridge.
Cool the potato slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn left and step forward to face the potato on the counter.
Place the slice of potato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To heat a potato slice and place it on the counter.
